@startuml UserMenus
actor "System User" as User
participant "SPA (Frontend)" as Frontend
participant "Backend Module(s)" as Backend

User -> Frontend: Authenticate / Login (credentials or token)
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: Request: GET /menu (with user role)
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: Response: 200 OK + Menu Data (based on role)
deactivate Backend
Frontend --> User: Render menus based on role
deactivate Frontend
@enduml